{"tid":1059492,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇四川大地震香港政府捐左90億","createTime":"2019-03-13T07:02:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T07:25:15.000Z","uid":60594,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8aea29f40e9edcc925a328c825d30adc51ce04f4","tid":1059492,"uid":60594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T07:02:39.000Z","msg":"香港，至2008年5月14日，各組織及個人捐款1.42062億港元，其中李嘉誠以及李嘉誠基金會、長江集團、和記黃埔等共計捐款人民幣1億3000萬，曾憲梓1000萬港元，恒生銀行200萬港元，滙豐銀行1000萬港元[13]。至地震發生一年後，香港立法會共撥款捐達90億港元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地永遠冇天災 四川我又未去過 點解要用納稅人嘅錢捐<br />\n上次打風都冇人捐錢比我地 <br />\n香港人其實唔洗咁好心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5eff732bbbf614fe946942bec80ad49e940f763","tid":1059492,"uid":196924,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T07:06:26.000Z","msg":"咁又唔好話永遠冇天災<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家8~10號風球都多咗好多<br />\n只係香港人抗災能力痴線, 10號風都阻止唔到大家返工咁解"},{"pid":"570ab41ce189b6d060d890f5e9e0bf34aa054a28","tid":1059492,"uid":202354,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e5eff732bbbf614fe946942bec80ad49e940f763","tid":1059492,"uid":196924,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T07:06:26.000Z","msg":"咁又唔好話永遠冇天災<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家8~10號風球都多咗好多<br />\n只係香港人抗災能力痴線, 10號風都阻止唔到大家返工咁解"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T07:18:47.000Z","msg":"啲風一年勁過一年，好期待今年會帶啲咩驚喜比香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88fb5e3aaef8e9f461cb4d77322dec754a45adb6","tid":1059492,"uid":173271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T07:20:13.000Z","msg":"俾錢買病毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acc48ca7cc5ec0aa8a7dbb60ce4564c70807516a","tid":1059492,"uid":100016,"like":8,"dis